This file serves as a short-term roadmap for the project.
It will be updated regularly as new features are planned and implemented.


Upcoming Features
=================
+ Add items to grow worm
+ Enable pausing and restarting
+ Add basic obstacles
+ Add message area
+ Track and display points
+ Add a second worm that moves randomly
+ Give second worm basic intelligence to avoid obstacles
+ Animate items
+ Enable items to move around autonomously


Implemented
===========
2016-01-17 - Add collision detection for worm body
2016-01-17 - Add boundaries so worm cannot go off screen
2016-01-14 - Control a worm with the arrow keys
2016-01-14 - Control a rectangle with the arrow keys
2015-12-21 - Display an empty window
